      <bioghist id="aspace_dd9d07a0a5c2ee934350b99313f8dec0">
         <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
         <p>The Public Interfaces Committee (PIC) of the Yale University Library is charged with improving the usability of the library's electronic interfaces, with particular emphasis on the maintenance, ongoing evaluation, and design of the library's online catalog and web site.</p>  
      </bioghist>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_ec5fade8452494c5dba0057168e3ff8a">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of electronic files documenting the changes made to the library web site ("Front Door") by the Yale Library Public Interfaces Committee (PIC).</p>  
      </scopecontent>
  
